reviewText: l love it....it's a very good workout

I disagree with the other reviewer..I found this set to be fun & Jaana is a great teacher. The music was fun and I had a great cardio workout. It includes 4 45 minute workouts hip hop, latin, sexy sculpt & disco. I would recommend these to anyone!

I got this for free luckily, I had a gift card and did not need anything else to buy, it also would have expired in a few days, so I figured why not give this a try.

This Xtreme Cardio Dance is a waste of time and there is nothing extreme or cardio about it either. Good thing it was discontinued.
